<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.215259>
    dc:description "FIGURES 23 – 29. Ufo nipponicus, new species, female: 23, mesosoma, lateral view, 24, pronotum, anterior view, 25, propleuron, anterior view, 26, mesoscutum, dorsal view, 27, mesoscutellum, dorsal view, 29, metascutellum and propodeum, posterodorsal view, 29, metasoma, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/215259/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.215262>
    dc:description "FIGURES 40 – 47. Ufo koreanus Melika, Pujade-Villar & Choi, female: 40 – 41, head: 40, anterior view, 41, dorsal view. 42, antenna. 43, mesosoma, lateral view, 44, mesoscutum, dorsal view, 45, mesoscutellum, dorsal view, 46, mesosoma, ventral view, 47, metasoma, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/215262/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.215258>
    dc:description "FIGURES 18 – 22. Ufo nipponicus, new species, female: 18 – 21, head: 18, anterior view, 19, dorsal view, 20, posterior view. 21, lateral view. 22, antenna." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/215258/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.215263>
    dc:description "FIGURES 48 – 52. Host oak galls of Ufo spp.: 48, Cerroneuroterus vonkuenburgi, asexual galls, 49, C. monzeni, asexual galls, 50, C. nawai, asexual galls, 51, Trichagalma acutissimae, asexual galls, 52, Andricus kunugifoliae, asexual galls (photos by G. Csóka)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/215263/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

